pciids
------------------------------------------
This is a public repository of all known ID's used in PCI devices: ID's of
vendors, devices, subsystems and device classes.

Runtime requirements:

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  cygport-0.37.7-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pciutils/pciids

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pciutils/pciids/raw/006181e2c5d5b9a3b57d252aa5b3d827971d41a9/pci.ids

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack pciids-20260524-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./pciids-20260524-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pciids-20260524-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/pciids-20260524-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(pciids)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/pciids.README
  /usr/share/misc/pci.ids

------------------

